{"tid":1855573,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有北上度歲市民擔心受感染提早回港","createTime":"2020-02-01T07:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T07:44:58.000Z","uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eef32015351feaa1150c149cbbbffd022219e44c","tid":1855573,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=378298\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378298&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Ijk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=342934dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378298&h=47c7faa0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=378298</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】因應疫情擴大，農曆年出入境人數大減，但仍有市民回鄉度歲或到內地遊玩。假期即將結束，有人提早返港，亦有人感受到內地疫情嚴峻，擔心受感染而提早結束行程。<br />\n<br />\n農曆年假即將結束，為免人多擠擁，一些回鄉度歲的市民提早回港。在羅湖口岸，過關前同樣要填寫健康申報表，大堂到處是填表的人，之後排隊過關。<br />\n<br />\n湖北之外，廣東省最多確診個案。陳先生一家大小年廿九去惠州探親，原本打算留一星期，最後都決定提早回港。<br />\n<br />\n他們逗留了兩天，就決定走。<br />\n<br />\n不理口岸人多，有人仍然零防範。<br />\n<br />\n香港入境關口亦有貼出告示，提醒湖北省居民或14日內到過湖北的人士不可入境。"},{"pid":"c453b43a83bc20aebda22c90891f8e04b0711c6d","tid":1855573,"uid":49018,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:07:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咪撚躝落嚟"},{"pid":"fc79baf442972e52139557ac2517ba070c3faae9","tid":1855573,"uid":22822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"上去一家團聚多幾日啦，咁撚大鍋都仲好走上去，咁撚重視親情咪燃落嚟"},{"pid":"0e22d661612cbf0cd3a199707497e2644d408dae","tid":1855573,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:13:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d6b7ba80bb4953e1d22ffcc59dac2a6f13994a80","tid":1855573,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hoT3W7D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=htt